  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x3BF0", "zh": "哼……！好厚的脸皮！！"},
  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x3C10", "zh": "哇啊啊！你这、你这！！"},
  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x3C30", "zh": "休想得逞！！"},
